NB. =========================================================
NB. Utilities

NB.*tomusigma v Converts from N[0,1] to N[mu,sigma]
tomusigma=: 4 : 0
  'mu sigma'=. x
  mu + sigma*y
)

NB.*tostd v Converts from N[mu,sigma] to N[0,1]
tostd=: 4 : 0
  'mu sigma'=. x
  (y-mu)%sigma
)

NB.*runif01 v Uniform random deviates
runif01=: ?@$0:

